        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n@Reviewers: For some reason, Jenkins can't seems to pick up the {project-name}-{stream}-docker-golang-shell-daily template which is already present in global-templates-golang.yaml [1]. So it errors in logs as 'jenkins_jobs.errors.JenkinsJobsException: Failed to find suitable template named '{project-name}-{stream}-docker-golang-shell-daily'. \n\nAny idea why it doesn't get picked up?\n\n[1] - https://git.onap.org/ci-management/tree/jjb/global-templates-golang.yaml#n133",
